// LastDay function definition
(int yr & int mth) >> new LastDay:
    mth >> check:
        is 2:
            (yr % 400 == 0) || (yr % 4 == 0 && yr % 100 != 0) >> check:
                is true: 29 >> Return.
                else:    28 >> Return.
            ..
        is 4: 30 >> Return.
        is 6: 30 >> Return.
        is 9: 30 >> Return.
        is 11: 30 >> Return.
        else: 31 >> Return.
    ..
..

// Test for (i = 1; i < month; i++) total += lastDay(year, i);
2024 >> year.
5 >> month. // May 1st -> sum of Jan, Feb, Mar, Apr (31 + 29 + 31 + 30 = 121)
0 >> total.

[1, month - 1] >> Range >> do each:
    total + (year & @ >> LastDay) >> total.
..

"{0}年{1}月までの経過日数: {2}日" & year & month & total >> Format >> Display.
